This is a map made from scratch unlike verson 2 which was an edit of bhop_mist.
I have spent a long time on this as it has been created with accuracy and optimisation.

This map is designed to be easy before anyone saids it's too easy.
There are custom sounds and textures and a song at the end.

I would like to say a great thanks to aoki who pointed me in the right direction when it came to optimise the map so thankyour for that.

Thank you for the people who tested the map while i was creating it .Bn , Chimpy , aoki , 5-6-ace , byron the bulb , If i missed you off please message me =)
